Summary
  Defines the number of colors a gradient can contain.
Description
  TJvXPGradientColors is used for the Colors property of TJvXPGradient and defines the allowable range
  of colors in the gradient.
See Also
  TJvXPGradient

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPGradientStyle
