  TJvXPGradient

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPGradientStyle.gsLeft
  The gradient starts at the left edge of the image and moves to the right.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPGradientStyle.gsTop
  The gradient starts at the top edge of the image and moves down.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPGradientStyle.gsRight
  The gradient starts at the right edge of the image and moves left.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPGradientStyle.gsBottom
  The gradient starts at the bottom edge of the image and moves upwards.

