@@TJvXPStyle
Summary
  Class that is used to describe the way styles are handled in an XP style control.
Description
  TJvXPStyle is used by XP style controls to control how the style of the control is managed. Either
  the control handles its own style changes or the style is controlled from a style manager.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyle.Theme
Summary
  Defines the theme of the control.
Description
  Use Theme to modify the visual appearance of a control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyle.UseStyleManager
Summary
  Determines if the style and theme is controlled from a style manager.
Description
  Use UseStyleManager to control whether the style of a control is controlled from the control itself
  or from a central style manager component. UseStyleManager only have any effect if the <LINK
  TJvXPCustomStyleControl.StyleManager, StyleManager> property of the control is set to a valid
  TJvXPStyleManager.
See Also
  TJvXPStyleManager

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyleManager
<TITLEIMG TJvXPStyleManager>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.XPControls
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A component that manages the theme and style of any number of connected controls.
Description
  Use a TJvXPStyleManager when you want to control the visual appearance of several or all XP style
  controls on a form. By setting each XP controls StyleManager to point to a TJvXPStyleManager, you can
  change all associated controls from one central location.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyleManager.OnThemeChanged
Summary
  Called when the theme of the style manager changes.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnThemeChanged event when you want to take specific action when the theme of
  the style manager changes. For example, use it to change the visual appearance of other controls that
  cannot be associated with the style manager but still need to synchronize their looks with the XP
  controls.
See Also
  TJvXPStyleManager.Theme

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyleManager.RegisterControls
Summary
  Adds controls to the style manager.
Description
  RegisterControls is called automatically by XP controls when their StyleManager property is set to a
  valid style manager. All registered controls changes together when the style manager's Theme property
  changes.
Parameters
  AControls - an array of XP style controls
See Also
  <LINK UnregisterControls>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyleManager.Theme
Summary
  Defines the current theme.
Description
  Use Theme to set and change the current theme for all connected controls.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvXPStyleManager.UnregisterControls
Summary
  Removes controls from the style manager.
Description
  Controls call UnregisterControls automatically when their StyleManager property is changed.
Parameters
  AControls - an array of controls to remove from the internal list of registered controls.
See Also
  <LINK RegisterControls>

